    - tcp_bbr: init pacing rate on first RTT sample
  * [SRU][Zesty] Fix lscpu segfault on ARM64 with SMBIOS v2.0 (LP: #1716483)
    - arm64: kernel: restrict /dev/mem read() calls to linear region

