    - ipv6: Prevent overrun when parsing v6 header options
  * CVE-2017-9076
    - ipv6/dccp: do not inherit ipv6_mc_list from parent
  * CVE-2017-9077
    - ipv6/dccp: do not inherit ipv6_mc_list from parent
